<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<style>
body {
  font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
  background-color: black;
}

* {
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

/* Add padding to containers */
.container {
  padding: 16px;
  background-color: white;
}

/* Full-width input fields */
input[type=text], input[type=password] {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 15px;
  margin: 5px 0 22px 0;
  display: inline-block;
  border: none;
  background: #f1f1f1;
}

input[type=text]:focus, input[type=password]:focus {
  background-color: #ddd;
  outline: none;
}

/* Overwrite default styles of hr */
hr {
  border: 1px solid #f1f1f1;
  margin-bottom: 25px;
}

/* Set a style for the submit button */
.login_button {
  background-color: #4571d0;
  color: white;
  padding: 16px 20px;
  margin: 8px 0;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  width: 100%;
  opacity: 0.9;
}

.registerbtn:hover {
  opacity: 1;
}

/* Add a blue text color to links */
a {
  color: dodgerblue;
}

/* Set a grey background color and center the text of the "sign in" section */
.signin {
  background-color: #f1f1f1;
  text-align: center;
}

.footer {
   position: fixed;
   left: 0;
   bottom: 0;
   width: 100%;
   background-color: black;
   color: white;
   text-align: center;
}

</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
<form action="" method="POST">
    <h1>Administrator login</h1>
    <hr>
    <h2>Detected 3 incorrect login attempts!</h2>

    <b><h3>You need to successfully solve 3 captchas in a row</h3></b>

    
    <label for="usr"></label><br>
    <img src="data:image/png;base64,">
    <input type="text" placeholder="value" name="captcha" id="captcha" value="" required>
    

    

    <button type="submit" class="login_button"><b>Log in</b></button>
  
</form>
<hr>
    

    

      </div>

<div class="footer">
  <p>Proudly hosted, maintained, and developed by <b>SecureSolaCoders ©</b></p>
</div>

  font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
  background-color: black;
}

* {
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

/* Add padding to containers */
.container {
  padding: 16px;
  background-color: white;
}

/* Full-width input fields */
input[type=text], input[type=password] {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 15px;
  margin: 5px 0 22px 0;
  display: inline-block;
  border: none;
  background: #f1f1f1;
}

input[type=text]:focus, input[type=password]:focus {
  background-color: #ddd;
  outline: none;
}

/* Overwrite default styles of hr */
hr {
  border: 1px solid #f1f1f1;
  margin-bottom: 25px;
}

/* Set a style for the submit button */
.login_button {
  background-color: #4571d0;
  color: white;
  padding: 16px 20px;
  margin: 8px 0;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  width: 100%;
  opacity: 0.9;
}

.registerbtn:hover {
  opacity: 1;
}

/* Add a blue text color to links */
a {
  color: dodgerblue;
}

/* Set a grey background color and center the text of the "sign in" section */
.signin {
  background-color: #f1f1f1;
  text-align: center;
}

.footer {
   position: fixed;
   left: 0;
   bottom: 0;
   width: 100%;
   background-color: black;
   color: white;
   text-align: center;
}

</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
<form action="" method="POST">
    <h1>Administrator login</h1>
    <hr>
    <label for="usr"><b>Username</b></label>
    <input type="text" placeholder="Firstname" name="username" id="username" value="rachel" required>

    <label for="psw"><b>Password</b></label>
    <input type="password" placeholder="Password" name="password" id="password" value="juanita" required>
    <hr>

    <button type="submit" class="login_button"><b>Log in</b></button>
  
</form>
    
    <p class="error"><strong>Error:</strong> Invalid username or password
    
      </div>

<div class="footer">

  padding: 16px;
  background-color: white;
}

/* Full-width input fields */
input[type=text], input[type=password] {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 15px;
  margin: 5px 0 22px 0;
  display: inline-block;
  border: none;
  background: #f1f1f1;
}

input[type=text]:focus, input[type=password]:focus {
  background-color: #ddd;
  outline: none;
}

/* Overwrite default styles of hr */
hr {
  border: 1px solid #f1f1f1;
  margin-bottom: 25px;
}

/* Set a style for the submit button */
.login_button {
  background-color: #4571d0;
  color: white;
  padding: 16px 20px;
  margin: 8px 0;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  width: 100%;
  opacity: 0.9;
}

.registerbtn:hover {
  opacity: 1;
}

/* Add a blue text color to links */
a {
  color: dodgerblue;
}

/* Set a grey background color and center the text of the "sign in" section */
.signin {
  background-color: #f1f1f1;
  text-align: center;
}

.footer {
   position: fixed;
   left: 0;
   bottom: 0;
   width: 100%;
   background-color: black;
   color: white;
   text-align: center;
}

</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
<form action="" method="POST">
    <h1>Administrator login</h1>
    <hr>
    <label for="usr"><b>Username</b></label>
    <input type="text" placeholder="Firstname" name="username" id="username" value="rachel" required>

    <label for="psw"><b>Password</b></label>
    <input type="password" placeholder="Password" name="password" id="password" value="danielle1" required>
    <hr>

    <button type="submit" class="login_button"><b>Log in</b></button>
  
</form>
    
    <p class="error"><strong>Error:</strong> Invalid username or password
    
      </div>

  width: 100%;
  padding: 15px;
  margin: 5px 0 22px 0;
  display: inline-block;
  border: none;
  background: #f1f1f1;
}

input[type=text]:focus, input[type=password]:focus {
  background-color: #ddd;
  outline: none;
}

/* Overwrite default styles of hr */
hr {
  border: 1px solid #f1f1f1;
  margin-bottom: 25px;
}

/* Set a style for the submit button */
.login_button {
  background-color: #4571d0;
  color: white;
  padding: 16px 20px;
  margin: 8px 0;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  width: 100%;
  opacity: 0.9;
}

.registerbtn:hover {
  opacity: 1;
}

/* Add a blue text color to links */
a {
  color: dodgerblue;
}

/* Set a grey background color and center the text of the "sign in" section */
.signin {
  background-color: #f1f1f1;
  text-align: center;
}

.footer {
   position: fixed;
   left: 0;
   bottom: 0;
   width: 100%;
   background-color: black;
   color: white;
   text-align: center;
}

</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
<form action="" method="POST">
    <h1>Administrator login</h1>
    <hr>
    <h2>Detected 3 incorrect login attempts!</h2>

    <b><h3>You need to successfully solve 3 captchas in a row</h3></b>

    <img src="data:image/png;base64,">

  border: none;
  background: #f1f1f1;
}

input[type=text]:focus, input[type=password]:focus {
  background-color: #ddd;
  outline: none;
}

/* Overwrite default styles of hr */
hr {
  border: 1px solid #f1f1f1;
  margin-bottom: 25px;
}

/* Set a style for the submit button */
.login_button {
  background-color: #4571d0;
  color: white;
  padding: 16px 20px;
  margin: 8px 0;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  width: 100%;
  opacity: 0.9;
}

.registerbtn:hover {
  opacity: 1;
}

/* Add a blue text color to links */
a {
  color: dodgerblue;
}

/* Set a grey background color and center the text of the "sign in" section */
.signin {
  background-color: #f1f1f1;
  text-align: center;
}

.footer {
   position: fixed;
   left: 0;
   bottom: 0;
   width: 100%;
   background-color: black;
   color: white;
   text-align: center;
}

</style>
</head>

  outline: none;
}

/* Overwrite default styles of hr */
hr {
  border: 1px solid #f1f1f1;
  margin-bottom: 25px;
}

/* Set a style for the submit button */
.login_button {
  background-color: #4571d0;
  color: white;
  padding: 16px 20px;
  margin: 8px 0;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  width: 100%;
  opacity: 0.9;
}

.registerbtn:hover {
  opacity: 1;
}

/* Add a blue text color to links */
a {
  color: dodgerblue;
}

/* Set a grey background color and center the text of the "sign in" section */
.signin {
  background-color: #f1f1f1;
  text-align: center;
}

.footer {
   position: fixed;
   left: 0;
   bottom: 0;
   width: 100%;
   background-color: black;
   color: white;
   text-align: center;
}

</style>
</head>
<body>

<form action="" method="POST">
    <h1>Administrator login</h1>
    <hr>
    <label for="usr"><b>Username</b></label>
    <input type="text" placeholder="Firstname" name="username" id="username" value="rachel" required>

    <label for="psw"><b>Password</b></label>
    <input type="password" placeholder="Password" name="password" id="password" value="nightmare" required>

  border: 1px solid #f1f1f1;
  margin-bottom: 25px;
}

/* Set a style for the submit button */
.login_button {
  background-color: #4571d0;
  color: white;
  padding: 16px 20px;
  margin: 8px 0;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  width: 100%;
  opacity: 0.9;
}

.registerbtn:hover {
  opacity: 1;
}

/* Add a blue text color to links */
a {
  color: dodgerblue;
}

/* Set a grey background color and center the text of the "sign in" section */
.signin {
  background-color: #f1f1f1;
  text-align: center;
}

.footer {
   position: fixed;
   left: 0;
   bottom: 0;
   width: 100%;
   background-color: black;
   color: white;
   text-align: center;
}

</style>
</head>
<body>

    <hr>

  background-color: #4571d0;
  color: white;
  padding: 16px 20px;
  margin: 8px 0;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  width: 100%;
  opacity: 0.9;
}

.registerbtn:hover {
  opacity: 1;
}

/* Add a blue text color to links */
a {
  color: dodgerblue;
}

/* Set a grey background color and center the text of the "sign in" section */
.signin {
  background-color: #f1f1f1;
  text-align: center;
}

.footer {
   position: fixed;
   left: 0;
   bottom: 0;
   width: 100%;
   background-color: black;
   color: white;
   text-align: center;
}

</style>
</head>

  width: 100%;
  opacity: 0.9;
}

  opacity: 1;

  text-align: center;

   position: fixed;
   left: 0;

   text-align: center;

  width: 100%;

  border: none;
  background: #f1f1f1;

  background-color: #ddd;
  outline: none;

  border: 1px solid #f1f1f1;
  margin-bottom: 25px;
}

.login_button {
  background-color: #4571d0;
  color: white;
  padding: 16px 20px;
  margin: 8px 0;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  width: 100%;

}

  opacity: 1;

}

  text-align: center;
}

   position: fixed;
   left: 0;
   bottom: 0;
   width: 100%;

   color: white;

<style>
body {
  font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
  background-color: black;
}

* {
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

/* Add padding to containers */
.container {
  padding: 16px;
  background-color: white;
}

/* Full-width input fields */
input[type=text], input[type=password] {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 15px;
  margin: 5px 0 22px 0;
  display: inline-block;
  border: none;
  background: #f1f1f1;
}

input[type=text]:focus, input[type=password]:focus {
  background-color: #ddd;
  outline: none;
}

/* Overwrite default styles of hr */
hr {
  border: 1px solid #f1f1f1;
  margin-bottom: 25px;
}

/* Set a style for the submit button */
.login_button {
  background-color: #4571d0;
  color: white;
  padding: 16px 20px;
  margin: 8px 0;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  width: 100%;
  opacity: 0.9;
}

.registerbtn:hover {
  opacity: 1;
}

/* Add a blue text color to links */
a {
  color: dodgerblue;
}

/* Set a grey background color and center the text of the "sign in" section */
.signin {
  background-color: #f1f1f1;
  text-align: center;
}

.footer {
   position: fixed;
   left: 0;
   bottom: 0;
   width: 100%;
   background-color: black;
   color: white;
   text-align: center;
}

</style>
</head>

<style>
body {
  font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
  background-color: black;
}

  box-sizing: border-box;
}

/* Add padding to containers */
.container {
  padding: 16px;
  background-color: white;
}

/* Full-width input fields */
input[type=text], input[type=password] {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 15px;
  margin: 5px 0 22px 0;
  display: inline-block;
  border: none;
  background: #f1f1f1;
}

input[type=text]:focus, input[type=password]:focus {
  background-color: #ddd;
  outline: none;
}

/* Overwrite default styles of hr */
hr {
  border: 1px solid #f1f1f1;
  margin-bottom: 25px;
}

/* Set a style for the submit button */
.login_button {
  background-color: #4571d0;
  color: white;
  padding: 16px 20px;
  margin: 8px 0;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  width: 100%;
  opacity: 0.9;
}

.registerbtn:hover {
  opacity: 1;
}

a {
  color: dodgerblue;
}

/* Set a grey background color and center the text of the "sign in" section */
.signin {
  background-color: #f1f1f1;
  text-align: center;
}

.footer {
   position: fixed;
   left: 0;
   bottom: 0;
   width: 100%;
   background-color: black;
   color: white;
   text-align: center;
}

</style>

  background-color: black;

  box-sizing: border-box;
}

  padding: 16px;
  background-color: white;
}

  width: 100%;
  padding: 15px;
  margin: 5px 0 22px 0;
  display: inline-block;
  border: none;
  background: #f1f1f1;
}

input[type=text]:focus, input[type=password]:focus {
  background-color: #ddd;
  outline: none;
}

/* Overwrite default styles of hr */
hr {
  border: 1px solid #f1f1f1;
  margin-bottom: 25px;
}

/* Set a style for the submit button */
.login_button {
  background-color: #4571d0;
  color: white;
  padding: 16px 20px;
  margin: 8px 0;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  width: 100%;
  opacity: 0.9;
}

.registerbtn:hover {
  opacity: 1;
}

a {
  color: dodgerblue;
}

/* Set a grey background color and center the text of the "sign in" section */
.signin {
  background-color: #f1f1f1;
  text-align: center;
}

.footer {
   position: fixed;
   left: 0;
   bottom: 0;
   width: 100%;
   background-color: black;
   color: white;
   text-align: center;
}

</style>

<style>
body {
  font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
  background-color: black;
}

  box-sizing: border-box;
}

/* Add padding to containers */
.container {
  padding: 16px;
  background-color: white;
}

/* Full-width input fields */
input[type=text], input[type=password] {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 15px;
  margin: 5px 0 22px 0;
  display: inline-block;
  border: none;
  background: #f1f1f1;
}

input[type=text]:focus, input[type=password]:focus {
  background-color: #ddd;
  outline: none;
}

/* Overwrite default styles of hr */
hr {
  border: 1px solid #f1f1f1;
  margin-bottom: 25px;
}

/* Set a style for the submit button */
.login_button {
  background-color: #4571d0;
  color: white;
  padding: 16px 20px;
  margin: 8px 0;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  width: 100%;
  opacity: 0.9;
}

.registerbtn:hover {
  opacity: 1;
}

/* Add a blue text color to links */
a {
  color: dodgerblue;
}

/* Set a grey background color and center the text of the "sign in" section */
.signin {
  background-color: #f1f1f1;
  text-align: center;
}

.footer {
   position: fixed;
   left: 0;
   bottom: 0;
   width: 100%;
   background-color: black;
   color: white;
   text-align: center;
}

</style>

  outline: none;

  border: 1px solid #f1f1f1;
  margin-bottom: 25px;

  background-color: #4571d0;
  color: white;

  margin: 8px 0;
  border: none;

  text-align: center;
}

   position: fixed;
   left: 0;
   bottom: 0;

  background-color: black;
}

  box-sizing: border-box;
}

  padding: 16px;
  background-color: white;
}

/* Full-width input fields */
input[type=text], input[type=password] {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 15px;
  margin: 5px 0 22px 0;
  display: inline-block;
  border: none;
  background: #f1f1f1;
}

input[type=text]:focus, input[type=password]:focus {
  background-color: #ddd;
  outline: none;
}

/* Overwrite default styles of hr */
hr {
  border: 1px solid #f1f1f1;
  margin-bottom: 25px;
}

/* Set a style for the submit button */
.login_button {
  background-color: #4571d0;
  color: white;
  padding: 16px 20px;
  margin: 8px 0;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  width: 100%;
  opacity: 0.9;
}

.registerbtn:hover {
  opacity: 1;
}

a {
  color: dodgerblue;
}

/* Set a grey background color and center the text of the "sign in" section */
.signin {
  background-color: #f1f1f1;
  text-align: center;
}

.footer {
   position: fixed;
   left: 0;
   bottom: 0;
   width: 100%;
   background-color: black;
   color: white;
   text-align: center;
}

</style>

<style>
body {
  font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
  background-color: black;
}

  box-sizing: border-box;
}

/* Add padding to containers */
.container {
  padding: 16px;
  background-color: white;
}

/* Full-width input fields */
input[type=text], input[type=password] {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 15px;
  margin: 5px 0 22px 0;
  display: inline-block;
  border: none;
  background: #f1f1f1;
}

input[type=text]:focus, input[type=password]:focus {
  background-color: #ddd;
  outline: none;
}

/* Overwrite default styles of hr */
hr {
  border: 1px solid #f1f1f1;
  margin-bottom: 25px;
}

/* Set a style for the submit button */
.login_button {
  background-color: #4571d0;
  color: white;
  padding: 16px 20px;
  margin: 8px 0;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  width: 100%;
  opacity: 0.9;
}

.registerbtn:hover {
  opacity: 1;
}

a {
  color: dodgerblue;
}

/* Set a grey background color and center the text of the "sign in" section */
.signin {
  background-color: #f1f1f1;
  text-align: center;
}

.footer {
   position: fixed;
   left: 0;
   bottom: 0;
   width: 100%;
   background-color: black;
   color: white;
   text-align: center;
}

</style>

<html>
<head>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<style>
body {
  font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
  background-color: black;
}

* {
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

/* Add padding to containers */
.container {
  padding: 16px;
  background-color: white;
}

/* Full-width input fields */
input[type=text], input[type=password] {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 15px;
  margin: 5px 0 22px 0;
  display: inline-block;
  border: none;
  background: #f1f1f1;
}

input[type=text]:focus, input[type=password]:focus {
  background-color: #ddd;
  outline: none;
}

/* Overwrite default styles of hr */
hr {
  border: 1px solid #f1f1f1;
  margin-bottom: 25px;
}

/* Set a style for the submit button */
.login_button {
  background-color: #4571d0;
  color: white;
  padding: 16px 20px;
  margin: 8px 0;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  width: 100%;
  opacity: 0.9;
}

.registerbtn:hover {
  opacity: 1;
}

/* Add a blue text color to links */
a {
  color: dodgerblue;
}

/* Set a grey background color and center the text of the "sign in" section */
.signin {
  background-color: #f1f1f1;
  text-align: center;
}

.footer {
   position: fixed;
   left: 0;
   bottom: 0;
   width: 100%;
   background-color: black;
   color: white;
   text-align: center;
}

</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
<form action="" method="POST">
    <h1>Administrator login</h1>
    <hr>
    <label for="usr"><b>Username</b></label>
    <input type="text" placeholder="Firstname" name="username" id="username" value="bart" required>

    <label for="psw"><b>Password</b></label>
    <input type="password" placeholder="Password" name="password" id="password" value="muffin" required>
    <hr>

    <button type="submit" class="login_button"><b>Log in</b></button>
  
</form>
    
    <p class="error"><strong>Error:</strong> Invalid username or password
    
      </div>

<div class="footer">

</div>

  font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
  background-color: black;
}

* {
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

/* Add padding to containers */
.container {
  padding: 16px;
  background-color: white;
}

/* Full-width input fields */
input[type=text], input[type=password] {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 15px;
  margin: 5px 0 22px 0;
  display: inline-block;
  border: none;
  background: #f1f1f1;
}

input[type=text]:focus, input[type=password]:focus {
  background-color: #ddd;
  outline: none;
}

/* Overwrite default styles of hr */
hr {
  border: 1px solid #f1f1f1;
  margin-bottom: 25px;
}

/* Set a style for the submit button */
.login_button {
  background-color: #4571d0;
  color: white;
  padding: 16px 20px;
  margin: 8px 0;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  width: 100%;
  opacity: 0.9;
}

.registerbtn:hover {
  opacity: 1;
}

/* Add a blue text color to links */
a {
  color: dodgerblue;
}

/* Set a grey background color and center the text of the "sign in" section */
.signin {
  background-color: #f1f1f1;
  text-align: center;
}

.footer {
   position: fixed;
   left: 0;
   bottom: 0;
   width: 100%;
   background-color: black;
   color: white;
   text-align: center;
}

</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
<form action="" method="POST">
    <h1>Administrator login</h1>
    <hr>
    <label for="usr"><b>Username</b></label>
    <input type="text" placeholder="Firstname" name="username" id="username" value="jamie" required>

    <label for="psw"><b>Password</b></label>
    <input type="password" placeholder="Password" name="password" id="password" value="unicorn" required>
    <hr>

    <button type="submit" class="login_button"><b>Log in</b></button>
  
</form>
    
    <p class="error"><strong>Error:</strong> Invalid username or password
    
      </div>

<div class="footer">
  <p>Proudly hosted, maintained, and developed by <b>SecureSolaCoders ©</b></p>
</div>
</body>

  padding: 16px;
  background-color: white;
}

/* Full-width input fields */
input[type=text], input[type=password] {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 15px;
  margin: 5px 0 22px 0;
  display: inline-block;
  border: none;
  background: #f1f1f1;
}

input[type=text]:focus, input[type=password]:focus {
  background-color: #ddd;
  outline: none;
}

/* Overwrite default styles of hr */
hr {
  border: 1px solid #f1f1f1;
  margin-bottom: 25px;
}

/* Set a style for the submit button */
.login_button {
  background-color: #4571d0;
  color: white;
  padding: 16px 20px;
  margin: 8px 0;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  width: 100%;
  opacity: 0.9;
}

.registerbtn:hover {
  opacity: 1;
}

/* Add a blue text color to links */
a {
  color: dodgerblue;
}

/* Set a grey background color and center the text of the "sign in" section */
.signin {
  background-color: #f1f1f1;
  text-align: center;
}

.footer {
   position: fixed;
   left: 0;
   bottom: 0;
   width: 100%;
   background-color: black;
   color: white;
   text-align: center;
}

</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
<form action="" method="POST">
    <h1>Administrator login</h1>
    <hr>
    <h2>Detected 3 incorrect login attempts!</h2>

    <b><h3>You need to successfully solve 3 captchas in a row</h3></b>

    

    
    <label for="usr"></label>Describe the shape below (circle, square, or triangle)<br><br>
    <img src="data:image/png;base64,">
    <input type="text" placeholder="shape" name="captcha" id="captcha" value="" required>
    

    <button type="submit" class="login_button"><b>Log in</b></button>
  
</form>
<hr>
    

    

      </div>

<div class="footer">

  width: 100%;
  padding: 15px;
  margin: 5px 0 22px 0;
  display: inline-block;
  border: none;
  background: #f1f1f1;
}

input[type=text]:focus, input[type=password]:focus {
  background-color: #ddd;
  outline: none;
}

/* Overwrite default styles of hr */
hr {
  border: 1px solid #f1f1f1;
  margin-bottom: 25px;
}

/* Set a style for the submit button */
.login_button {
  background-color: #4571d0;
  color: white;
  padding: 16px 20px;
  margin: 8px 0;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  width: 100%;
  opacity: 0.9;
}

.registerbtn:hover {
  opacity: 1;
}

/* Add a blue text color to links */
a {
  color: dodgerblue;
}

/* Set a grey background color and center the text of the "sign in" section */
.signin {
  background-color: #f1f1f1;
  text-align: center;
}

.footer {
   position: fixed;
   left: 0;
   bottom: 0;
   width: 100%;
   background-color: black;
   color: white;
   text-align: center;
}

</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
<form action="" method="POST">
    <h1>Administrator login</h1>
    <hr>
    <label for="usr"><b>Username</b></label>
    <input type="text" placeholder="Firstname" name="username" id="username" value="jamie" required>

    <label for="psw"><b>Password</b></label>
    <input type="password" placeholder="Password" name="password" id="password" value="emmanuel" required>
    <hr>

    <button type="submit" class="login_button"><b>Log in</b></button>

  border: none;
  background: #f1f1f1;
}

input[type=text]:focus, input[type=password]:focus {
  background-color: #ddd;
  outline: none;
}

/* Overwrite default styles of hr */
hr {
  border: 1px solid #f1f1f1;
  margin-bottom: 25px;
}

/* Set a style for the submit button */
.login_button {
  background-color: #4571d0;
  color: white;
  padding: 16px 20px;
  margin: 8px 0;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  width: 100%;
  opacity: 0.9;
}

.registerbtn:hover {
  opacity: 1;
}

/* Add a blue text color to links */
a {
  color: dodgerblue;
}

/* Set a grey background color and center the text of the "sign in" section */
.signin {
  background-color: #f1f1f1;
  text-align: center;
}

.footer {
   position: fixed;
   left: 0;
   bottom: 0;
   width: 100%;
   background-color: black;
   color: white;
   text-align: center;
}

</style>
</head>

  outline: none;
}

/* Overwrite default styles of hr */
hr {
  border: 1px solid #f1f1f1;
  margin-bottom: 25px;
}

/* Set a style for the submit button */
.login_button {
  background-color: #4571d0;
  color: white;
  padding: 16px 20px;
  margin: 8px 0;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  width: 100%;
  opacity: 0.9;
}

.registerbtn:hover {
  opacity: 1;
}

/* Add a blue text color to links */
a {
  color: dodgerblue;
}

/* Set a grey background color and center the text of the "sign in" section */
.signin {
  background-color: #f1f1f1;
  text-align: center;
}

.footer {
   position: fixed;
   left: 0;
   bottom: 0;
   width: 100%;
   background-color: black;
   color: white;
   text-align: center;
}

</style>
</head>
<body>

<form action="" method="POST">
    <h1>Administrator login</h1>
    <hr>

    <b><h3>You need to successfully solve 3 captchas in a row</h3></b>

  border: 1px solid #f1f1f1;
  margin-bottom: 25px;
}

/* Set a style for the submit button */
.login_button {
  background-color: #4571d0;
  color: white;
  padding: 16px 20px;
  margin: 8px 0;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  width: 100%;
  opacity: 0.9;
}

.registerbtn:hover {
  opacity: 1;
}

/* Add a blue text color to links */
a {
  color: dodgerblue;
}

/* Set a grey background color and center the text of the "sign in" section */
.signin {
  background-color: #f1f1f1;
  text-align: center;
}

.footer {
   position: fixed;
   left: 0;
   bottom: 0;
   width: 100%;
   background-color: black;
   color: white;
   text-align: center;
}

</style>
</head>
<body>

    <h1>Administrator login</h1>

.login_button {
  background-color: #4571d0;
  color: white;
  padding: 16px 20px;
  margin: 8px 0;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  width: 100%;
  opacity: 0.9;
}

.registerbtn:hover {
  opacity: 1;
}

/* Add a blue text color to links */
a {
  color: dodgerblue;
}

/* Set a grey background color and center the text of the "sign in" section */
.signin {
  background-color: #f1f1f1;
  text-align: center;
}

.footer {
   position: fixed;
   left: 0;
   bottom: 0;
   width: 100%;
   background-color: black;
   color: white;
   text-align: center;
}

</style>
</head>

  cursor: pointer;
  width: 100%;
  opacity: 0.9;
}

.registerbtn:hover {
  opacity: 1;
}

  color: dodgerblue;
}

.signin {
  background-color: #f1f1f1;
  text-align: center;
}

.footer {
   position: fixed;
   left: 0;
   bottom: 0;
   width: 100%;
   background-color: black;
   color: white;
   text-align: center;
}

</style>

  width: 100%;
  padding: 15px;

  display: inline-block;
  border: none;
  background: #f1f1f1;
}

  background-color: #ddd;
  outline: none;
}

hr {
  border: 1px solid #f1f1f1;
  margin-bottom: 25px;
}

.login_button {
  background-color: #4571d0;
  color: white;
  padding: 16px 20px;
  margin: 8px 0;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  width: 100%;
  opacity: 0.9;
}

  opacity: 1;
}

a {
  color: dodgerblue;
}

  background-color: #f1f1f1;
  text-align: center;
}

   position: fixed;
   left: 0;
   bottom: 0;
   width: 100%;

   color: white;
   text-align: center;

<style>
body {
  font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
  background-color: black;
}

* {
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

/* Add padding to containers */
.container {
  padding: 16px;
  background-color: white;
}

/* Full-width input fields */
input[type=text], input[type=password] {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 15px;
  margin: 5px 0 22px 0;
  display: inline-block;
  border: none;
  background: #f1f1f1;
}

input[type=text]:focus, input[type=password]:focus {
  background-color: #ddd;
  outline: none;
}

/* Overwrite default styles of hr */
hr {
  border: 1px solid #f1f1f1;
  margin-bottom: 25px;
}

/* Set a style for the submit button */
.login_button {
  background-color: #4571d0;
  color: white;
  padding: 16px 20px;
  margin: 8px 0;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  width: 100%;
  opacity: 0.9;
}

.registerbtn:hover {
  opacity: 1;
}

/* Add a blue text color to links */
a {
  color: dodgerblue;
}

/* Set a grey background color and center the text of the "sign in" section */
.signin {
  background-color: #f1f1f1;
  text-align: center;
}

.footer {
   position: fixed;
   left: 0;
   bottom: 0;
   width: 100%;
   background-color: black;
   color: white;
   text-align: center;
}

</style>
</head>

}

  width: 100%;

  display: inline-block;
  border: none;
  background: #f1f1f1;
}

  background-color: #ddd;
  outline: none;
}

  border: 1px solid #f1f1f1;
  margin-bottom: 25px;
}

.login_button {
  background-color: #4571d0;
  color: white;
  padding: 16px 20px;
  margin: 8px 0;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  width: 100%;
  opacity: 0.9;
}

.registerbtn:hover {
  opacity: 1;
}

a {
  color: dodgerblue;
}

  background-color: #f1f1f1;
  text-align: center;
}

.footer {
   position: fixed;
   left: 0;
   bottom: 0;
   width: 100%;

   color: white;
   text-align: center;

  background-color: black;

  box-sizing: border-box;
}

  padding: 16px;
  background-color: white;
}

/* Full-width input fields */
input[type=text], input[type=password] {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 15px;
  margin: 5px 0 22px 0;
  display: inline-block;
  border: none;
  background: #f1f1f1;
}

input[type=text]:focus, input[type=password]:focus {
  background-color: #ddd;
  outline: none;
}

/* Overwrite default styles of hr */
hr {
  border: 1px solid #f1f1f1;
  margin-bottom: 25px;
}

/* Set a style for the submit button */
.login_button {
  background-color: #4571d0;
  color: white;
  padding: 16px 20px;
  margin: 8px 0;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  width: 100%;
  opacity: 0.9;
}

.registerbtn:hover {
  opacity: 1;
}

/* Add a blue text color to links */
a {
  color: dodgerblue;
}

/* Set a grey background color and center the text of the "sign in" section */
.signin {
  background-color: #f1f1f1;
  text-align: center;
}

.footer {
   position: fixed;
   left: 0;
   bottom: 0;
   width: 100%;
   background-color: black;
   color: white;
   text-align: center;
}

</style>
